   It might be longer because you are turning the subject response clock on 
which has a timeout of 1500 ms but your display after the clock on is only 
about 1000 ms (two 500 ms frames plus one tick for the superfluous "/!;" ) 
so DMDX can still be waiting for a response after the display has finished.

